cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Cosmoplot, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: Cosmoplot
abstract: >-
  A science-first, Sun-centered web app that maps nearby exoplanet systems in 3D
  from live NASA Exoplanet Archive data and derives each world's physics
  (interior, atmosphere, climate, escape, and detectability) from published
  relations, with the provenance of every value kept visible.
type: software
authors:
